Inside My Creative Core

I’m a Full-stack Software Engineer with 3+ years of experience building and scaling high performance web applications.Proven track record of leading development teams, optimizing performance, and consistently delivering projects ahead of deadlines. Highly proficient in React, Next.js, Node.js, JavaScript, TypeScript, and Docker, with expertise in crafting user-focused solutions serving thousands of active users. Experienced in integrating AI and LLM-powered systems to enhance product capabilities. Passionate about developing modern SaaS platforms, improving user experience, and writing clean, maintainable, and efficient code.
I enjoy collaborating with teams, solving real-world problems, and turning complex ideas into clean, engaging designs.
